    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Last Keeper</strong> —— 一款心理恐怖游戏，光仍是生命与疯狂之间唯一的界限。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>你开始在一座偏远岛屿上担任灯塔守望者。</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每天都遵循固定的例行工作：保持秩序、维护机械、监视灯塔的光芒与雾号。只要灯光还在，船只就能找到方向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005700/extras/c7f0911776d776c2f1b3c25e65f80bc0.poster.avif?t=1771833097\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005700/extras/c7f0911776d776c2f1b3c25e65f80bc0.webm?t=1771833097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005700/extras/c7f0911776d776c2f1b3c25e65f80bc0.mp4?t=1771833097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >工作与生存：清理房间、修理设备并获取食物。岛屿不会原谅疏忽——你的生存只取决于自己。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005700/extras/3f6d819dd6ffa09ccc0e7e921ec823fc.poster.avif?t=1771833097\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005700/extras/3f6d819dd6ffa09ccc0e7e921ec823fc.webm?t=1771833097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005700/extras/3f6d819dd6ffa09ccc0e7e921ec823fc.mp4?t=1771833097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >接收求救信号，回应船只的呼叫，并做出决定，左右它们的命运。有时，电波中传来的远不止应有的内容……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005700/extras/f6257892d1efe15351ca01fba67e7f82.poster.avif?t=1771833097\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005700/extras/f6257892d1efe15351ca01fba67e7f82.webm?t=1771833097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005700/extras/f6257892d1efe15351ca01fba67e7f82.mp4?t=1771833097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >规划航线，标记危险区域，引导船只进入安全的港湾。地图上的一次失误，可能会夺走一条生命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005700/extras/3a3a308b1f005986ae4f6420115ac501.poster.avif?t=1771833097\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005700/extras/3a3a308b1f005986ae4f6420115ac501.webm?t=1771833097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005700/extras/3a3a308b1f005986ae4f6420115ac501.mp4?t=1771833097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >岛屿的秘密：探索废弃建筑，寻找前任守望者的痕迹，逐步揭开这个不愿被理解之地的历史。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005700/extras/3aaba2f03312d7e7d0834fa9844faf03.poster.avif?t=1771833097\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005700/extras/3aaba2f03312d7e7d0834fa9844faf03.webm?t=1771833097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005700/extras/3aaba2f03312d7e7d0834fa9844faf03.mp4?t=1771833097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >夜晚是一场考验：黑暗逼近，收音机中响起诡异的声音，而你的工作一刻也不能停止。不要让灯塔熄灭，也不要让雾号沉寂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005700/extras/d421cc08209b0bdc8315f980cd34089e.poster.avif?t=1771833097\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005700/extras/d421cc08209b0bdc8315f980cd34089e.webm?t=1771833097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005700/extras/d421cc08209b0bdc8315f980cd34089e.mp4?t=1771833097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>基于真实谜团：灵感来源于海洋传说与海洋文学作品。</i></h2>",
